title: Watch Nick Saban, Alabama football players thank fans for support at Tide homecoming pep rally
text:
Published By: Al.com: Tuscaloosa - Today 
The head coach and select players thanked the crowd and each gave them a hearty "Roll Tide" on the Quad on Friday....
